OL,3,CAbortion clinic buffer zones to come
OL,4,Cinto effect next month
OL,6,FBuffer zones banning protests outside
OL,7,Fof abortion clinics in England and
OL,8,FWales will come into force next month.
OL,10,FThe new law prohibits protests within
OL,11,F150 metres of clinics or hospitals
OL,12,Fproviding abortion services.
OL,14,FIt will be illegal for someone to do
OL,15,Fanything deemed to intentionally or
OL,16,Frecklessly influence someone's
OL,17,Fdecision to use abortion services,
OL,18,Fobstruct them, or cause harassment or
OL,19,Fdistress to someone using or working
OL,20,Fat these locations.
