OL,3,CAbortion clinic buffer zones to come
OL,4,Cinto effect next month
OL,6,FThe maximum penalty for anyone
OL,7,Fconvicted will be an unlimited fine.
OL,9,FThe legislation was given royal assent
OL,10,Fover a year ago, but its
OL,11,Fimplementation was delayed under the
OL,12,FConservative government due to the
OL,13,Fissue of silent prayer.
OL,15,FPro-choice campaigners had raised
OL,16,Fconcerns that the law would be watered
OL,17,Fdown in practice if silent prayer was
OL,18,Fnot also banned.
