OL,3,CAbortion clinic buffer zones to come
OL,4,Cinto effect next month
OL,6,FSafeguarding minister Jess Phillips
OL,7,Fsaid: "The right to access abortion
OL,8,Fservices is a fundamental right for
OL,9,Fwomen in this country, and no one
OL,10,Fshould feel unsafe when they seek to
OL,11,Faccess this.
OL,13,F"We will not sit back and tolerate
OL,14,Fharassment, abuse and intimidation as
OL,15,Fpeople exercise their legal right to
OL,16,Fhealthcare, which is why we have fast-
OL,17,Ftracked this measure to get it up and
OL,18,Frunning without further delay.
