OL,6,F"For too long abortion clinics have
OL,7,Fbeen without these vital protections,
OL,8,Fand this Government is determined to
OL,9,Fdo all we can do to make this country
OL,10,Fa safer place for women."
OL,12,FIn Scotland, legislation creating
OL,13,Fbuffer zones around abortion clinics
OL,14,Fis due to come into force on September
OL,15,F24.
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland has had safe access
OL,18,Fzones outside clinics offering
OL,19,Fabortions since September last year.
